text: Major General Vasyl Vasylovych Durdynets (, born 27 September 1937) is a Ukrainian politician. He was the Acting Prime Minister of Ukraine for a short time in July 1997."DURDYNETS, Vasyl Vasylyovych", Government Portal (Ukraine Government), retrieved 5 February 2010 ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Ukraine Category:Ukrainian military people
